Various setup details.  Just so I don't forget.  Should turn these into proper instructions at some point.  

sudo pip install pyserial

There's going to be something to do with pycrc or python-crypto here
download pycrc from https://www.tty1.net/pycrc/index_en.html (sorry about the awful download page)
extract the archive

-- this might be good enough:  sudo pip install pycrypto --


Plug in and turn on the hypnocube, then do ls -la /dev/cu.usb*


